{"type": "article", "id": 18801, "title": "开花的躺椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-10T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160208u7rhVqz3KmDnB6OH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一张可以自由滚动的躺椅，其实可以将它看成一张床。椅子背后有一个弧形框架，可以随着人身体的重心移动而移动，就像是一张半贴合身体的软垫。椅子上开满了绿色的“花朵”，是用毛毡和多层泡沫做的，非常亮丽，也有花园的舒适气氛。新西兰惠林顿维多利亚大学的同学一起设计了这张座椅，它很适合放在年轻人房间里。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061602069WGbcpCMhwIzfnAZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.46454768\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160207a2uPp3lEy5OxdceZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57823961\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061602075t7OaTH4mfrsoSPi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160208BM6xT8GNm240Dt7L.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}